246
00:16:07,912 --> 00:16:09,311
Merci.

247
00:16:09,981 --> 00:16:11,414
Venez vous asseoir.

248
00:16:13,684 --> 00:16:14,981
Asseyez-vous.

249
00:16:15,386 --> 00:16:16,853
Assis !

250
00:16:18,823 --> 00:16:21,690
